ZH: 我需要一个帮手来完成这个项目。
EN: I need a helper to finish this project.

ZH: 他是我的得力帮手，总是帮我解决问题。
EN: He is my capable assistant, always helping me solve problems.

ZH: 请大家找一个帮手把这些箱子搬进去。
EN: Please find a helper to move these boxes inside.

ZH: 她是我的忠实帮手，从不辜负我的信任。
EN: She is my loyal assistant, never betraying my trust.

ZH: 孩子们需要成年人的帮手来学习新的技能。
EN: Children need the help of adults to learn new skills.

ZH: 请让我介绍一下我的新帮手，她叫小张。
EN: Let me introduce my new assistant, her name is Xiaozhang.

ZH: 昨天我花了很长时间找一个拿起桌子的帮手。
EN: Yesterday I spent a long time finding a helper to pick up the table.

ZH: 在学校里，老师就是我们的知识帮手。
EN: In school, teachers are our knowledge helpers.

ZH: 我的弟弟是我最亲密的帮手，在我需要的时候总是陪在我身边。
EN: My younger brother is my closest helper, always by my side when I need him.

ZH: 老板派了两个帮手帮忙清理仓库。
EN: The boss sent two helpers to help clean up the warehouse.

ZH: 他过去是我的得力帮手，但现在他已经升职做经理了。
EN: He used to be my capable assistant, but now he has been promoted to manager.

ZH: 请向警察寻求帮手，以便找到失踪的孩子。
EN: Please seek help from the police to find the missing child.

ZH: 她是公司的重要帮手，负责处理所有的财务事务。
EN: She is an important helper in the company, responsible for handling all financial affairs.

ZH: 有时候，找个帮手来分担工作会事半功倍。
EN: Sometimes, having a helper to share the work can be twice as effective.

ZH: 我现在正面临很多挑战，需要一个帮手来一起应对。
EN: I am facing many challenges now and need a helper to face them together.

ZH: 作为领导，你必须懂得团队合作，与帮手共同努力。
EN: As a leader, you must understand teamwork and work together with helpers.

ZH: 开始一项新工程时，需要找到合适的帮手来支持你。
EN: When starting a new project, it is important to find the right helpers to support you.

ZH: 她是一个优秀的帮手，总是能按时完成任务。
EN: She is an excellent helper, always able to complete tasks on time.

ZH: 我们需要一个熟练的帮手来修理这台机器。
EN: We need a skilled helper to repair this machine.
